  "_comment": "Shared parity corpus for the audit-status validator. BOTH the .mjs validator test (scripts/__tests__/audit-status-lib.test.mjs) and the TS validator test (shared/src/audit-status.test.ts) load THIS file and assert identical verdicts, so the two language ports of the canonical logic cannot diverge. integrityOk = checkIntegrity(doc).ok; approved = evaluateApproval(doc).approved; reasonSubstr = a substring that must appear in at least one reason when the verdict is a failure. Every approved-shaped case carries a full valid build-evidence block (compiler + 64-hex source-tree/creation/runtime hashes + immutable_references + approved_chain_ids) so a failing case isolates exactly the one field under test.",
